Archive: Stephen Hendry hits his first Crucible maximum break
Stephen Hendry makes his first Crucible 147 maximum break against Jimmy White in 1995.The seven-time world champion's maximum break made him only the third person to score a 147 at the Crucible, following Canada'sCliff Thorburn in 1983andWhite himself in 1992.Available to UK users only.